Little Cup June 2013 News

[head]

[page]

<h3>Congratulations iss!</h3>

<p>Posted by Charmander on <strong>Jun 20, 2013</strong>.</p>

<p>After blarajan being promoted to tiering and C&C leader, Little Cup was in need for another moderator, and <a href="/forums/member.php?u=34723">iss</a> was immediately appointed! Congrats to our new staff member, iss! This new addition to the LC staff team will certainly push LC in a better direction.</p>

<h3>LC-Themed Smogcast!</h3>

<p>Posted by Charmander on <strong>Jun 18, 2013</strong>.</p>

<p>Once again, the Little Cup community has brought together some of its most knowledgeable players as panelists on the new LC Smogcast. Join iss, Elevator Music, prem, and blarajan in an exciting discussion on the LC metagame, tiering, and forum projects as well as a Q&A session with questions submitted by everyday users! View the Smogcast <a href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4qaEnbqBIgU">here</a>. If you still have unanswered questions after watching the podcast, the <a href="/forums/showthread.php?t=85472">LC SQSA thread</a> should be your next stop!</p>

<h3>New LC Tier Leader!</h3>

<p>Posted by Charmander on <strong>Jun 14, 2013</strong>.</p>

<p>After the previous head of Little Cup stepped down, user <a href="http://www.smogon.com/forums/member.php?u=59999">blarajan</a> was promoted the Little Cup tiering leader and head of C&C. blarajan will also lead the community in shifting over to the sixth generation metagame once it is released. He has been extremely hard working, and the future of LC will continue to be in good hands. Congratulations blarajan!</p>